OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry and mostly cloudy evening, though
OL,7,Fa few late sunny spells are possible,
OL,8,Fmainly in the southeast. Overnight,
OL,9,Fconditions will remain dry and largely
OL,10,Fcloudy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA little light rain possible
OL,13,Fin the north and west at first.
OL,14,FOtherwise mainly dry and cloudy with a
OL,15,Ffew bright or sunny intervals breaking
OL,16,Fthrough in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
